Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:15.73,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}終將在那片海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:22.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}微笑著和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:27.64,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}我們共同活過的那天
