Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:30.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,跟提督 還有各位相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:42.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:10.76,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:14.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,盡力做好自己能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,請看著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:34.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,所以 所以一定要記著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,之後再…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:54.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我出發了
