Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}伝え切れない夢 仰ぐ空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}僕が届けるよ 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:42.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}雨 終會停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:55.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}至今心仍留在那裡 我與你擁抱的那夜晚
