Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:18.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}回憶映在天空 殘陽如血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:24.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}春日與五月 跨過山與海
