Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}訴不盡的夢想 仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我會傳達的 向未來
